deal 7 cards to each payer

game loop:
    next player
    show center
    show hand
    select cards to play on center row 1
    check if cards can be played
    yes? play cards
    select cards to play on center row 2
    check if cards can be played
    yes? play cards
    ...

    is player hand empty?
        yes:
            end round
            add points 
            check win 200 points
        no:
            continue
            

